> On Tue, Aug 27, 2019 at 08:01:39AM +0200, Michal Hocko wrote:
>> On Mon 26-08-19 16:15:38, Kirill A. Shutemov wrote:
>>>
>>> Unmapped completely pages will be freed with current code. Deferred split
